organization.description:
A private, non-for-profit organization whose mission is to provide people with disabilities the assistance and support necessary to enable them to live valued lives in the community.

Services Include:
* Adult Day Training
* Companion Services
* In-Home Support Services
* ICF/DD (Intermediate Care Facility for the Developmentally Disabled)
* Residential Habilitation
* Respite Care
* Supported Employment
organization.name: SUNRISE COMMUNITY
